title: Stocks to Watch - What's Ahead in the Markets this Week
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Ben Levisohn discuss the outlook for financial markets, interest rates, airlines, Tesla, Goldman Sachs, and other companies reporting second-quarter earnings.
